    "The patients were able to perform most of the cardiac rehabilitation exercises within or",
    "In this scoping review, thirteen studies were identified that reported the application of AI-driven VRehab platforms in the delivery of rehabilitation services to patients in their homes.",
    "The studies made use of a variety of sensors to collect data about patients in different modalities.",
    "The collected data were used by AI algorithms to provide guidance and feedback to patients or report patients' performance to clinicians.",
    "A variety of effectiveness evaluation metrics revealed that AI-driven home-based VRehab was effective in improving patients' health outcomes compared to non-AI-driven home-based VRehab (n = 1) and in-person rehabilitation (n = 4)."
  ]
}